                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-52-off279 t18310630-52-crimeloc281"></join> on the 18th of May; I left my tools there safe, and on the following morning I missed two planes and a screw-driver - William Anderson worked with me.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310630-52-person483">
                  CHARLES 
                  CLARKE
               <interp inst="t18310630-52-person483" type="surname" value="CLARKE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310630-52-person483" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
