                  </persName>
            . I am a Police-constable. On the morning of the 19th of May I was on duty in the New-road, and saw the prisoner at twenty minutes before five o'clock carrying these three planes; I found on him two screw-drivers - one, I believe, belongs to himself; he said he was going to work in the fields - I know nearly all the buildings there, and I asked who he worked for; he could not tell me - he afterwards said he brought them from a house next to a shop; I went there, and found the prosecutor.</p>
